### Variables Globales
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@auth = Basic tu_usuario tu_password

### Obtener todos los platos (Paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{auth}}

### Obtener plato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes/1
Authorization: {{auth}}

### Crear un nuevo plato
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
    "name": "Pasta Carbonara",
